Common Interview Questions
Array vs ArrayList?
Answer:
Array → fixed size, faster, primitive support
ArrayList → dynamic, more flexible, only objects

How does ArrayList grow?
When capacity is full:
newCapacity = oldCapacity + (oldCapacity >> 1)
That’s 1.5x growth

Why is insertion slow in middle?
Because elements shift:
O(n)

Is ArrayList thread-safe?
No.
Use:
Collections.synchronizedList()
or
CopyOnWriteArrayList

